dc_title_s: Bayfield County [Wisconsin] Water-Table Map and Water Well Database
dc_description_s: This report provides information about well construction, groundwater flow, and resulting implications for well susceptibility in Bayfield County, Wisconsin. The work follows an earlier groundwater study that focused on two agricultural areas within Bayfield County.
dct_provenance_s: Wisconsin Geological and Natural History Survey
dc_creator_sm: Wisconsin Geological and Natural History Survey
